{"tid":835443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空防升級！美批准對台百億軍售 提供F-16等備件","createTime":"2018-09-25T02:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T02:09:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b838b17fd06a5d7ffe36a3b0ccb68a673e47f88d","tid":835443,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-25/656/20180925001125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-09-25%2F656%2F20180925001125.jpg&h=5c4d93fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-16V戰機的資料照。（洛克希德馬丁公司）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部24日說，國務院批准對台灣軍售3.3億美元（約101億台幣）F-16戰機與其他軍機備用零件。<br />\n<br />\n據路透25日報導，美國國防安全合作署（Defense Security Cooperation Agency，DSCA）在聲明中說，國務院已批准，這次透過「對外軍售」（Foreign Military Sales，FMS），將出售「F-16、C-130、F-5、IDF與其他所有飛機系統與次系統備件，以及其他相關後勤元件和計畫支援」。<br />\n<br />\nDSCA在聲明中指出，這次對台軍售，將有助於「提升美國外交政策和國家安全」，也能提高受助國的安全與防衛能力，而這是區域政治穩定，軍事平衡和經濟發展的重要力量。不過DSCA也強調，這次軍售提案是維持台灣所需的防禦力，不會改變區域的軍事平衡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣多數的軍備都是美製，而台北一直希望，華府能出售包括新型戰機在內更先進的軍備。路透指出，美國對台軍售對美中關係是個刺激，北京深深懷疑華府對台灣的意圖。<br />\n<br />\n軍事專家說，兩岸間的軍力平衡向北京傾斜，除非美軍迅速支援，否則對岸可能會讓台灣無法招架。<br />\n<br />\n美國務院批准對台3.3億美元軍售 外交部：有助台海和平穩定<br />\n事實上，北京從未放棄武統台灣，美國防長馬提斯（Jim Mattis）6月訪問北京時，中國大陸國家主席習近平告訴他，「在涉及中國主權和領土完整問題上，我們的態度是堅定的也是明確的，老祖宗留下來的領土一寸也不能丟」。<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180925001085-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180925001085-260417&d=dIksk560s3FYQzljQpk5RZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=12f0cac8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180925001085-260417</a>"},{"pid":"30fc1bf92712aca406e8c3aa46e16379178ccf9a","tid":835443,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/100929_d2be60ada79e032da51e50a1dd32c8ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F100929_d2be60ada79e032da51e50a1dd32c8ab.png&h=e404dd3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係時事台開工啦<br />\n洗版超勤力</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/100142_f98dc8f2853db022e98f19ebc2336ad3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F100142_f98dc8f2853db022e98f19ebc2336ad3.png&h=f8dd0e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/100145_3b706ee8d2bb61d368cb9437dbe3ace9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F100145_3b706ee8d2bb61d368cb9437dbe3ace9.jpg&h=16bda88d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/100935_352211dd0eed621d8c2acc846904aafb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F100935_352211dd0eed621d8c2acc846904aafb.jpg&h=fc6715bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>講下政府點樣公然侮辱香港人好過啦</strong></span></span>"}]}